      "content": "i'm just so desperate to sleep. i've checked the forums and people say that taking melatonin with ambien is a common thing to do for bad insomnia. if i just take a small dose of melatonin, like maybe 1mg or 3mg, with my prescription, is that really going to be a problem? it feels way safer than just struggling through the night and being a zombie at work tomorrow while i wait for my doctor.",
